text: Nuria Ayala (born 28 March 1970) is a former synchronized swimmer from Spain. She competed in both the 1988 and 1992 Summer Olympics. == References == Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Spain Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 1992 Summer Olympics
